Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_clock(25.10)                                          reset_clock(25.10)

Name
       reset_clock - Removes previously created clock assertions

Syntax
       reset_clock

       {-all | <clock_list>}

       Removes previously created clock assertions.

Parameters
       -all   Removes all clocks in the design.

       <clock_list>
              Specifies  the  list  of clocks for which the clock assertion is
              removed.

Examples
              * The following commands reset a list of clocks and all  clocks,
                and display the results using the report_clocks command:

                report_clocks

                # Generates the following report:

                -----------------------------------------------------------------

                Clock Descriptions

                -----------------------------------------------------------------

                Attributes

                --------------------------------------------------------------------

                Clock   Name    Source    Period    Lead    Trail    Generated
                Propagated

                --------------------------------------------------------------------

                CK1          CLK1     20.000   0.000  10.000   n          n

                CK2          CLK1     10.000   0.000  5.000    n          n

                --------------------------------------------------------------------

                Generated-Clock Descriptions

                ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                Name     Generated    Master       Master-clock  Invert  Freq.
                Duty-Cycle   Edges   Edge-Shift

                        Source(pin) Source(pin)                     Multiplier

                ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                GCLK4     u8/Q          CLK4         CLK_W_4       n       1/2
                -           -       -

                reset_clock [get_clocks CK1]

                report_clocks

                -------------------------------------------------------------------

                Clock Descriptions

                --------------------------------------------------------------------

                Attributes

                --------------------------------------------------------------------

                Clock  Name    Source    Period    Lead    Trail     Generated
                Propagated

                ---------------------------------------------------------------------

                CK2          CLK1     10.000   0.000  5.000   n           n

                ---------------------------------------------------------------------

                ---------------------------------------------------------------------

                Generated-Clock Descriptions

                -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                Name    Generated     Master       Master-clock  Invert  Freq.
                Duty-Cycle  Edges  Edge-Shift

                       Source(pin)   Source(pin)                        Multi-
                plier

                --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                GCLK4   u8/Q          CLK4         CLK_W_4        n        1/2
                -           -      -

